  <h2>TL;DR — 3-Minute Summary</h2>
  
  <p><strong>If you're scheduling technicians for HVAC, plumbing, or electrical work in Wichita:</strong></p>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Monday.com:</strong> $9-$16/user/month — Great for office teams, but overkill for field crews. Calendar view is decent.</li>
    <li><strong>Housecall Pro:</strong> $49-$169/month — Built for contractors. Scheduling + dispatch + invoicing. Heavy on features, steep learning curve.</li>
